          <h3>Mahatma Gandhi National Rural Employment Guarantee Act (MGNREGA) of 2005</h3>
          <p>‚Ä¢ This is a rural wage employment programme in India. It provides for a legal guarantee of at least 100 days increased to 150 days now, of unskilled wage employment in a financial year to rural households whose adult members are willing to engage in unskilled manual work at a pre-determined minimum wage rate.<br><br>
              
              <b>The objectives of the Act are:</b><br>

